briefing.en-US: Seize the designated planet and establish a safe perimeter around it, so that the DSS can be safely upgraded there.
briefing.de-DE: Erobern Sie den vorgegebenen Planeten und errichten Sie einen sicheren Perimeter um ihn herum, damit die DRS dort aufgerüstet werden kann.
briefing.es-ES: Toma el planeta indicado y fija un perímetro seguro a su alrededor para que la E.E.D. pueda actualizarse con seguridad.
briefing.ru-RU: Захватите указанную планету и организуйте оборонительный периметр вокруг нее, чтобы здесь можно было безопасно улучшить ДКС.
briefing.fr-FR: Emparez-vous de la planète désignée et établissez un périmètre de sécurité autour, afin que la SSD soit sécurisée pendant son amélioration.
briefing.it-IT: Conquistare il pianeta designato e stabilire un perimetro di sicurezza intorno a esso, in modo che la SSD vi possa essere potenziata senza pericolo.
briefing.pl-PL: Przejmijcie wskazaną planetę i utwórzcie wokół niej bezpieczny perymetr, aby można było tam bezpiecznie ulepszać SKD.
briefing.zh-Hans: 占领指定星球，在它周围建立安全防线，确保民主空间站能够在此安全升级。
briefing.zh-Hant: 奪取指定星球的控制權並在周圍建立安全防線，確保能在該地安全升級DSS。

name.ja-JP: フェルカド・セカンダス

biome.name: Basic Swamp
biome.description: Tall, gnarled trees flourish across the surface of this forested world. Sunlight filters past dangling vines, to the saturated undergrowth below.

hazards.name: None
hazards.description: This planet's environment is not yet known, or has no environmental modifiers.

biome.name: Scorched Moor
biome.description: Scorching temperatures, high winds, and low precipitation cause a near-constant cycle of fires to sweep this planet, punctuated by short bursts of lush rebirth between infernos.

hazards.name: Fire Tornadoes
hazards.description: Planet is ravaged by deadly fire tornadoes.

biome.name: Acidic Badlands
biome.description: Dense, toxic fumes from deep within the planet's crust seep out of cracks in the earth and coat the ground in a sickly haze.

hazards.name: Acid Storms
hazards.description: Corrosive acid storms temporarily reduce armor effectiveness for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Deadlands
biome.description: The lifeless grey of this planet is interrupted only by the violet flowers that grow from strange, parasitic outcroppings.

hazards.name: Thick Fog
hazards.description: Dense fog lightly reduce visibility for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Desert Dunes
biome.description: A blazing-hot desert planet, its rocky mesas are the sole interruptions to the endless sea of dunes.

hazards.name: Sandstorms
hazards.description: Dense sandstorms reduce mobility and greatly reduce visibility for both enemy and friendly units.

biome.name: Ionic Jungle
biome.description: The strange subversion of photosynthesis that sustains the oddly-hued flora that flourishes on this planet remains an intriguing mystery to Super Earth's greatest exo-biologists.

hazards.name: Ion Storms
hazards.description: Ion storms intermittently disable Stratagems.
